rows.label: xs07070100_MSG0002
rows.name: Why would these aliens...be THIS determined to destroy us?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07070100_MSG0003
rows.name:
Honestly? If I had to venture a guess...
I'd say they're afraid.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07070100_MSG0004
rows.name: They fear humans... They feel threatened.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07070100_MSG0005
rows.name: We threaten them? WE didn't blow up their planet![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07070100_MSG0006
rows.name:
WE didn't hunt them halfway across the galaxy
to wipe out their whole goddamn species![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07070100_MSG0008
rows.name: I'm sorry, it just...brings back a lot of emotions.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07070100_MSG0011
rows.name:
Colonel, with your permission,
my team will report back to the city.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07070100_MSG0012
rows.name: I can't thank you enough for your support.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07070100_MSG0014
rows.name:
Irina had a younger brother...
He was best friends with Gwin, actually.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07070100_MSG0015
rows.name:
But he...he didn't make it onto the White Whale.
We lost him when we lost Earth.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07070100_MSG0017
rows.name:
Everyone's got a story like that...
not that it makes it any easier.[ST:wait ]
